description:
As a user
  I want to login
  So that I can access MyRockwell
name: Login

steps.name: User navigates to the myRockwell site
User is not logged in
User should navigate to the sign in page
User enters username and password
User clicks sign in
User should be directed to myRockwell home page

description:
As a user I need to verify the Apps details page
   for mobile, browser and desktop apps
name: Verify Apps details Page

elements.name: User verifies Apps details page for Mobile, Web & Desktop Apps

steps.name: the user clicks on the menu button
the User clicks on App Store
the user should navigate to the App store landing page
user is able to view the different Mobile apps
user clicks on any of the apps
user is on the App details page
user is able to view the App title
user is able to view the Save to My Apps button
user is able to view the Select Platform button
user is able to view the App Description
user is able to view other App details such as "Support","Languages","Requirements" section

elements.name: User verifies Apps details page for Mobile, Web & Desktop Apps

steps.name: the user clicks on the menu button
the User clicks on App Store
the user should navigate to the App store landing page
user is able to view the different Web apps
user clicks on any of the apps
user is on the App details page
user is able to view the App title

As a user
    I want to use the menu sign out button
    to sign out of myRockwell account

the user clicks on the menu button
The user clicks on the Sign Out link
User should navigate to the sign in page
